Furthermore, to quantitatively compare the impacts of different land-use transition patterns, this study constructed a continuous \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
